templateAssets.content: Competency (successfully completing the third college semester or fifth college quarter) is required in one foreign language to fulfill graduation requirements for this major.
Due to high demand, admission to SDSU is highly competitive. General admission information is available at: http://arweb.sdsu.edu/es/admissions/transfers/index.html.
